<p><span class="youtube">
<object type="application/x-shockwave-flash" width="480" height="295" data="http://www.youtube.com/v/wuKJVZRDjRo?color1=d6d6d6&amp;color2=f0f0f0&amp;border=0&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=en&amp;autoplay=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;iv_load_policy=3&amp;showsearch=0&amp;rel=0&amp;hd=1">
