<param name="wmode" value="transparent" />
</object>
</span></p>
<p>Here&#8217;s my question for fellow interaction designers and information  architects:</p>
<blockquote><p>Would the level of detail control actually be useful in your (re)design work, or is it just a gimmick?</p>
</blockquote>
<p>I am not entirely convinced that the benefits outweigh the added  complexity. Feel free to post your comments below or contact me on  Twitter via <a title="Jussi Pasanen (@jopas) on Twitter" rel="nofollow" href="http://twitter.com/jopas">@jopas</a> or <a title="Volkside Wirify (@wirify) on Twitter)" rel="nofollow" href="http://twitter.com/wirify">@wirify</a>. Thanks again!</p>
<p>
